RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT A.CONTRACT_REF_NO, A.USER_REF_NO, A.MODULE_CODE, A.CONTRACT_CCY, A.DEPARTMENT_CODE, A.PRODUCT_CODE, A.COUNTERPARTY, B.FACILITY_NAME, B.CUSIP_NO, B.EXTERNAL_CUSIP_NO, B.TREASURY_SOURCE, C.CUSTOMER_NAME1, D.PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT A, OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER B, OLTMS_CUSTOMER C, OLTMS_PRODUCT D WHERE A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = B.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND A.LATEST_VERSION_NO = B.VERSION_NO AND C.CUSTOMER_NO = A.COUNTERPARTY AND D.PRODUCT_CODE = A.PRODUCT_CODE
